StorySetUp_key1: Aap ek nayi Project directory **Stories** banaiye
StorySetUp_key2: Apne Stories directory mein navigate kijiye
StorySetUp_key3: Stories directory mein navigate karne ke baad aap **git init** command run kijiye
StorySetUp_key4: Iss command ke baad **git** humare iss directory mein banaye hue content ko track karna shuru kar dega.
StorySetUp_key6: Git ke documentation mein ja kar **git init** command ke baare mein padhe
